values:
I started writing my Star Wars ff story saga over two years ago and I, admittedly, had a very long lapse before recently starting again.

6 months ago, I received a expletive-ridden mess of a comment on my old ff livejournal and replied to it in a bit of a huff. I rediscovered the comment plus my response today.

The comment: 'ya whore ya slut ya prostitute u have abandoned this story but it is only to be expected of a mother fuckin faliure like yourself all I have to say is that you had so many people routin for you but now i'm sure that we've all realized what a lousy piece of shit you truley are i think i speak on the behalf of everyone of your disappointed fans in saying this
Hoping that you burn in hell
Anonymous'

My 'witty' reply: I wasn't even aware this account existed anymore, but I couldn't prevent myself from logging on and congratulating you; it's a feat not to use punctuation once in a 50 odd word entry.

If you expect me to be at all offended or roused into action by this piece of written vomit, then you are sorely mistaken. Indeed, insults over the internet rarely offend me, but if you expected me to take seriously an entry which has the word 'truley' and the letter 'u' used in placed of the word 'you', then you are a bigger moron than this true...poetry you have posted implies.

Also, I'd suggest you talk to actual people, or, you know, get out a bit more or even perhaps read a book if my prior suggestions are a bit too 'out there' for you, if the lack of update on a fanfiction affects you this deeply.

Normally, I wouldn't reply to such a poorly worded, poorly executed tirade, but I felt that my, admittedly somewhat harsh, words might help you to be become- if not a better person, upon seeing the truly pathetic way you have depicted yourself- a person less inclined to spend 17 hours a day in front of a computer screen in your attic/basement/shed/nuclear bunker.

Peace and Ta Ta.

P.S. Actually, I have no preference to which of my parents I fuck, so next time, instead of 'mother fuckin' can you please used 'parent fucking'? Let's not discriminate against fathers, eh? As far as I see it, incest is incest.

Thanks for your time, you kinky bitch.

Both the sheer ridiculousness of that comment and my own, frankly arsehole-y, reply made me 'lolz.' All I can say is that I was foolish and younger then...6 months younger, anyways.

Ta Ta; maybe the above displays of twatdom can give someone else a little giggle.
